in the beginning there were the charts huge 
sheets of cardboard resembling the visual aids a teacher uses to 
hold the class attention during a complicated lesson 
there was the timeline chart ranging from 1984 to 1990 with 
bright red and green blocks signifying the months or seasons when 
various witnesses said they had used drugs with mayor marion barry 
there was the lengthy locations chart subdivided into 
hotels businesses private residences government offices and 
boats 
and there was the drug activities with charles lewis chart 
neatly broken down by date place and drug 
barry himself subdued and somber sat directly under the lewis 
chart during closing arguments in his drug and perjury trial 
