<TEXT>
since the dawn of independence the sons of kuwait have aspired 
to freedom to participation with their arab brothers in the 
realization of the goals of the nation and the recuperation of 
usurped arab rights especially in palestine 
but the colonialists who had governed the country plundered its 
riches and humiliated the people before independence either 
directly or through the intermediary of their agents certain 
members of the alsabah family handed the reins of power to that 
same clique after independence letting them set up around their 
family an oligarchic despotic and corrupt power 
the fictitious institutions that this regime installed were not 
able to camouflage its reality which the people divined right from 
the first minute 
as the years went by the people became more and more convinced 
that this clique was determined to pursue its monopolization of 
power and its plundering of the riches of the country by 
collaborating with a small number of mercenaries relying 
principally on foreign forces 
falsification of elections authoritarianism persecution of 
patriotic personalities have always been characteristics of the 
regime of the alsabah family and of its stability the 
dissolution of the last parliament which put the despotism and the 
corruption of the regime under the limelight is a proof of the 
violation by this regime of the constitution and of the terrorism 
to which it had recourse every time it was cornered by the patriots 
this clique which was in the service of foreigners before 
independence remained so after independence it attached our 
interests and our wealth to foreign interests and even to certain 
known zionists it stained the reputation of our people putting 
hundreds of billions of dollars in foreign banks and in investments 
linked to zionist circles 
some of them in the alsabah family were known for their 
intransigence and corruption and were among the most faithful men 
of colonialism they collaborated and coordinated with it they 
intrigued and plotted in the vilest basest manner against the 
nation and its noble causes 
their last conspiracy was the one they hatched against iraq 
which assumed its responsibility to defend the eastern gateway of 
the arab nation kuwait and the countries of the persian gulf 
and suffered tremendous sacrifices to conserve their soil honor 
and dignity 
in this conspiracy with zionist and colonialist aims this 
alsabah family clique pulled off its mask manifesting its 
hostility to kuwait and the arab nation like a satellite in the 
pay of colonialism and zionism 
this is the reality of this clique that governed the country 
this is why the patriotic forces which rejected despotism 
injustice and corruption and resisted this regime attached to 
zionist and colonialist circles decided relying on gods will 
and the will of the people to assume power and topple this 
despotic satellite regime 
we declare the destitution from power of emir jaber alahmed 
alsabah and crown prince saad alabdullah alsabah as well as 
the dissolution of the national assembly and the formation of a 
free provisional government that will assume legislative and 
executive responsibilities during a transitional period and will 
organize free honest elections in order to elect an assembly that 
represents the people which will decide on a political system and 
other fundamental questions of the country 
the government finds that one of its primary obligations is to 
remedy the harm done by the deposed corrupt government to our 
brothers in iraq which backed us under difficult circumstances 
we consider the border issue with iraq by appealing to the 
principles of fraternity and arab national interests 
dear free citizens on this day a new era begins an era of 
serious action aimed at setting up the bases of freedom democracy 
and justice as well as true prosperity throughout society serious 
action is beginning to serve the objectives of the arab nation and 
deal with its fundamental issues 
the provisional government of free kuwait salutes you and calls 
on you to understand and sustain this uprising carried out by your 
free brothers 
the provisional government of free kuwait undertakes to protect 
the rights interests and security of foreigners living in kuwait 
and calls on them to carry out all the decisions and instructions 
issued by the government it will hit back vigorously against any 
attempt to destabilize the situation in kuwait or to carry out the 
plans of foreign forces 
the provisional government of free kuwait confirms its 
allegiance to all treaties in accordance with its arab islamic and 
world role in particular the charter of the arab league the 
treaty on common defense and economic cooperation among arab 
countries and the charter of the united nations as well as the 
