engagements visavis other countries and institutions and this 
following the principle of reciprocity it confirms it will carry 
out all reciprocal agreements and warns any foreign party not to 
interference in our internal affairs 
foreign forces allied with the expelled caste should know that 
the citizens of kuwait including arabs residing in this country 
will defend its soil its dignity and its uprising to the last drop 
