to excite the ambitions of suspect forces wanting to intervene 
directly or indirectly be it by their armies their fleets or by 
any other means these forces should know that kuwait is part of 
the arab nation and has at its side audacious experienced brothers 
who are ready to defend kuwait against any foreign aggression 
