me concerned for some time now he said 
government officials who would not be identified by name said 
the united states was told of the invasion at 830 pm washington 
time wednesday about 3 hours after it began 
bushs early morning order cut off virtually all commerce 
between the united states and iraq the only exceptions were 
publications and shipments to iraq of donated food clothing and 
medical supplies 
later in the day he issued a memorandum to agency heads barring 
any financial assistance loan guaratnees or export license to iraq 
iraq and kuwait together supply less than 10 percent of us oil 
imports according to us industry officials however the 
instability is certain to affect domestic oil prices 
bush summoned reporters before an early morning meeting with his 
