more than 200 kuwaitis were killed or wounded mainly from the 
emiri guard which bore the main brunt of the invasion kuwaits 
sheik saad alabdullah alsabah fled to safety in saudi arabia 
 
the forces iraq a country of more than 17 million has the 
arab worlds most battletrained army and had massed more than 
100000 soldiers on the kuwaiti border kuwait an oilrich 
citystate has 19 million residents 60 percent foreigners and 
